addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A <fr:em>category with representable maps</fr:em> or <fr:em>CwR</fr:em> is defined by <fr:link
type="local"
href="uemura-2021-thesis.xml"
addr="uemura-2021-thesis"
title="Abstract and Concrete Type Theories">Uemura</fr:link> to be a category <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex> with finite limits equipped with a pullback-stable class <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {R}_{\mathcal {C}}\subseteq  \mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}]]></fr:tex> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-0031.xml"
addr="jms-0031"
title="Exponentiable arrow">exponentiable arrows</fr:link> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:backmatter></fr:tree>